==English==

===Noun===
'''doomsday'''

===Pronounciation=== 
/"du:mzdeI/

===Etymology===
[[doom]] + [[day]]

===Definition===
# The day when God is expected to judge the world.
# The Day of Judgement; any day of decisive judgement or final dissolution.

===Combination=== 
*[[doomsday machine]] or [[doomsday bomb]] a hypothetical bomb capable of annihilating the world.

